4269bf64ca446d61c96.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0a/0d/1101812368_0:104:300:273_1920x0_80_0_0_f0640d0e9d3e617301048ed0b24c4635.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/" title="抄送 BY-SA 3.0">抄送 BY-SA 3.0</a> / / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：根据该国数字化转型部的空袭数据，周日深夜，包括基辅在内的乌克兰多个地区的空袭警报响起。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该部的在线地图显示，午夜过后不久，空袭警告在尼古拉耶夫、基洛沃格勒、切尔尼戈夫、苏梅和基辅等乌克兰地区以及乌克兰首都本身和乌克兰控制的赫尔松地区部分地区生效。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周日早些时候，空袭警报响起在第聂伯罗彼得罗夫斯克、哈尔科夫和波尔塔瓦地区，以及基辅控制的扎波罗热地区部分地区。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">自 10 月 10 日（克里米亚大桥恐怖袭击发生两天后）以来，俄罗斯对乌克兰基础设施实施了精确打击。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2月，乌克兰电网运营商Ukrenergo负责人表示，俄罗斯空袭对乌克兰能源基础设施造成的直接破坏可能高达数亿美元，经济损失达数十亿。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 22:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/air-raid-warnings-issued-in-multiple-regions-of-ukraine-1110757888.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/air-raid-warnings-issued-in-multiple-regions-of-ukraine-1110757888.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰能源公司</category><category>基辅</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>尼古拉耶夫</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Debt Ceiling Deal Faces Criticism and Uncertain Support from Key Democrats]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110757454" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/09/1110211152_0:0:2653:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_a7c346bec9218c21572787a177f223f3.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1110211134" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/debt-ceiling-deal-faces-criticism-and-uncertain-support-from-key-democrats-1110757454.html?share-img=1110211134"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / DANIEL SLIM</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">白宫于 2022 年 5 月 19 日在华盛顿特区亮相</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="The White House is seen on May 19, 2022 in Washington, DC - Sputnik International, 1920, 28.05.2023" title="白宫于 2022 年 5 月 19 日在华盛顿特区亮相" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/09/1110211152_0:278:2653:1770_1920x0_80_0_0_fdde1c596abf5ab7924a76d780a09d85.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/09/1110211152_0:278:2653:1770_640x0_80_0_0_4cb5d379a141f61dfd005978d0a72360.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/09/1110211152_0:278:2653:1770_1280x0_80_0_0_e1d307a4dd64923005823e821e76e96d.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/09/1110211152_0:278:2653:1770_1920x0_80_0_0_fdde1c596abf5ab7924a76d780a09d85.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / 丹尼尔斯利姆</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶戈尔·沙波瓦洛夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_shapovalov_egor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a><a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.shapovalov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">拜登总统和议长凯文麦卡锡之间达成的潜在债务上限协议遭到了主要民主党人的批评，包括那些对最终达成协议至关重要的人。保守派也表达了他们对临时协议某些内容的不满。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">经过数周的谈判后，达成了将债务上限提高两年并对联邦支出施加新上限的协议。由于双方立法者都批评该协议的某些方面，拜登和麦卡锡都可能面临各自党员的反对。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拜登将该<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/deal-in-principle-made-to-raise-us-debt-ceiling-before-default-1110644962.html" target="_blank">协议</a>描述为一种妥协，强调它避免了<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230508/what-should-americans-brace-for-on-the-brink-of-default-1110191569.html" target="_blank">灾难性的违约</a>，但承认并非所有人都会完全满意。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">众议院少数党领袖哈基姆杰弗里斯 (D-NY) 似乎对获得党内成员的足够支持以达成协议犹豫不决。虽然他预计会有一些民主党支持，但他承认他不知道确切的数字。他此前曾表示，民主党不会仅仅因为涉及白宫就自动支持一项协议。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">杰弗里斯补充说：“我们必须经历一个尊重众议院每一位成员以及他们充分理解所提出决议的能力的过程。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110757454" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/debt-ceiling-deal-faces-criticism-and-uncertain-support-from-key-democrats-1110757454.html?share-block=1110757654" data-title="&quot;We have to go through a process consistent with respecting every single member of the House of Representatives and their ability to fully understand the resolution that has been raised,&quot; Jeffries added."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一些著名的共和党人也对该交易做出了负面反应。众议员奇普罗伊 (R-TX) 将该协议称为“粪便三明治”，并对麦卡锡关于会议的大多数人对此感到兴奋的说法提出异议。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">杰弗里斯可能得不到由 100 多名成员组成的进步核心小组的支持。主席普拉米拉·贾亚帕尔 (D-WA) 在获得协议文本之前对她的投票表示不确定。她还警告说，核心小组可能不会支持该协议，这引起了国会和白宫民主党人的担忧。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该协议中一项有争议的条款是扩大某些美国人在食品券方面的工作要求，这引起了贾亚帕尔和其他民主党人的批评。但是，该法案的确切语言仍然未知，因此很难确定该条款是否会破坏交易。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">温和派众议员吉姆·海姆斯 (D-CT) 对该交易持保留态度，称他还不是明确的支持者。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “我还没有下定决心。整个企业都是一个腐败的企业，就以这种方式立法而言，我会听听总统和他的人民的论点是什么，但不，我不是一个明确的人是的，在这一点上投票，”海姆斯告诉美国媒体。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110757454" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/debt-ceiling-deal-faces-criticism-and-uncertain-support-from-key-democrats-1110757454.html?share-block=1110757657" data-title="&quot;I have not made up my mind. The whole enterprise is a corrupt enterprise, in terms of legislating this way, and I’m gonna listen to what the president’s and his people’s arguments are, but no, I’m anything but a clear yes vote at this point,&quot; Himes told US media."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">预计拜登总统和麦卡锡议长将讨论该协议，随后将公布立法文本。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 21:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/debt-ceiling-deal-faces-criticism-and-uncertain-support-from-key-democrats-1110757454.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/debt-ceiling-deal-faces-criticism-and-uncertain-support-from-key-democrats-1110757454.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>凯文麦卡锡</category><category>哈基姆杰弗里斯</category><category>民主党人</category><category>共和党人</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[IRGC Navy Chief Tells US to Get Out of Persian Gulf as Tensions Surge]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110756642" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/05/0c/1082868718_0:0:1200:675_1440x900_80_0_1_f98b9a31f411f8f14d41eb5f600995a0.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1082868230" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/irgc-navy-chief-tells-us-to-get-out-of-persian-gulf-as-tensions-surge-1110756642.html?share-img=1082868230"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / US NAVY</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">4 月 2 日，伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队海军 (IRGCN) Harth 55 号中锋接近海岸警卫队巡逻艇 USCGC Wrangell (WPB 1332) 船头，采取不安全且不专业的行动，迫使 Wrangell 号进行防御演习, 2021.</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="Iran’s Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps Navy (IRGCN) Harth 55, center, approaches the Coast Guard patrol boat USCGC Wrangell (WPB 1332) bow in an unsafe and unprofessional action forcing the Wrangell to conduct a defensive maneuver, April 2, 2021.  - Sputnik International, 1920, 28.05.2023" title="2021 年 4 月 2 日，伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队海军 (IRGCN) Harth 55（中）接近海岸警卫队巡逻艇 USCGC Wrangell（WPB 1332）船头，采取不安全和不专业的行动，迫使 Wrangell 号进行防御性演习。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/05/0c/1082868718_0:0:1200:675_1920x0_80_0_0_dc2332423160f9298bee2eed7920a56e.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/05/0c/1082868718_0:0:1200:675_640x0_80_0_0_55ba6aca13b374a1936dbfe2ea32395e.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/05/0c/1082868718_0:0:1200:675_1280x0_80_0_0_34402c7c29d650ebd5b221d483a4a59b.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/05/0c/1082868718_0:0:1200:675_1920x0_80_0_0_dc2332423160f9298bee2eed7920a56e.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / 美国海军</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">伊朗伊斯兰共和国已经积累了一系列本土防御系统来监测和保护其本国海岸外的水域，包括先进的远程巡航导弹、雷达和声纳设备。上个月，伊朗海军宣布，它迫使一艘试图偷偷穿过霍尔木兹海峡的美国弹道导弹潜艇浮出水面。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伊斯兰革命卫队 (IRGC) 海军司令阿里雷扎·坦西里 (Alireza Tangsiri) 表示，美国在波斯湾运营军舰是“大错特错”，伊朗“别无选择，只能坚持抵抗”或面对外部势力的毁灭性霸权. </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “你出现在我们地区是该死的错误，”这位指挥官本周在伊朗西南部德兹富尔举行的官方仪式上<a href="https://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2023/05/27/704169/IRGC-Navy-Rear-Admiral-Alireza-Tangsiri-US-military-presence-Persian-Gulf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">说</a>，该仪式纪念该市在 1980 年至 1988 年两伊战争期间的抵抗。 “波斯湾的安全由伊朗和该地区国家保证，不需要你或任何其他国家在场。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110756642" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/irgc-navy-chief-tells-us-to-get-out-of-persian-gulf-as-tensions-surge-1110756642.html?share-block=1110756644" data-title="“You are damn wrong to be present in our region,” the commander said, speaking an official ceremony in Dezful, southwestern Iran this week commemorating the city’s resistance during the Iran-Iraq War of 1980-1988. “The security of the Persian Gulf is assured by Iran and the countries of the region, and there is no need for you or any other country to be present.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">回顾 1979 年革命前的日子，美国和英国将伊朗视为“他们的殖民地”，坦西里<a href="https://www.farsnews.ir/news/14020305000587/%D8%B3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D9%86%DA%AF%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%A2%D9%85%D8%B1%DB%8C%DA%A9%D8%A7-%D8%BA%D9%84%D8%B7-%D9%85%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%AF-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B7%D9%82%D9%87-%D9%85%D8%A7-%D8%AD%D8%B6%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">说</a>，“抵抗的精神和动机赋予了伊朗民族尊严和荣誉，现在伊朗民族正在独立自主两英尺，抵抗力量破坏了敌人力量的方程式。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位指挥官还评论了媒体在伊朗与美国对抗中的重要性，指出福克斯新闻的记者可以嵌入海上的美国军舰上，并迅速传送有利于华盛顿的报道。因此，他说，虽然伊斯兰革命卫队海军和军方致力于“确保波斯湾的安全，但媒体必须参与这一安全并反映伊斯兰革命卫队海军和陆军的能力，以便世界了解波斯湾的安全波斯湾不需要外国人。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">唐西里本周的评论呼应了他在 4 月下旬表达的观点，当时他<a href="https://www.farsnews.ir/en/news/14020210000212/IRGC-Cmmander-US-Israel-Shld-Leave-Persian-Glf" target="_blank">强调</a>伊斯兰革命卫队海军准备“保护和保卫”波斯湾免受美国及其以色列盟友的侵害，并警告美国核武对当地生态系统构成的危险在该地区运行的动力军舰。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">本月早些时候，这位指挥官强调，伊斯兰革命卫队海军<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230513/irgc-navy-gets-ultra-long-range-cruise-missile-superior-to-the-tomahawk-1110323093.html" target="_blank">密切监视</a>在海湾地区活动的所有“敌方船只”，其能力“日益增强”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伊朗的本土<a href="https://www.aspi.org.au/report/critical-technology-tracker" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">技术创新</a>和军工基础知识近年来取得了巨大进步，中东国家开发了从先进的远程弹道导弹和巡航导弹和无人机到雷达、声纳防空和反舰防御的一切<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230427/iran-can-now-track-unique-radar-signature-of-individual-f-35-jets-1109893497.html" target="_blank">能够跟踪</a>美国最新武器系统的系统。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">上个月，伊朗海军<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230420/iranian-navy-forced-us-nuclear-submarine-to-surface-change-track-in-hormuz-strait-1109700784.html" target="_blank">报告</a>称成功迫使一艘美国俄亥俄级弹道导弹潜艇浮出水面，因为它试图在水下悄悄穿过霍尔木兹海峡。五角大楼否认其潜艇被迫浮出水面，指责德黑兰从事“破坏该地区稳定的虚假信息”。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 19:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/irgc-navy-chief-tells-us-to-get-out-of-persian-gulf-as-tensions-surge-1110756642.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/irgc-navy-chief-tells-us-to-get-out-of-persian-gulf-as-tensions-surge-1110756642.html<category>军队</category><category>中东</category><category>阿里雷萨·唐西里</category><category>波斯湾</category><category>伊斯兰共和国</category><category>伊斯兰革命卫队 (IRGC)</category><category>海军</category><category>我们</category><category>美国海军</category></item></channel></rss>